user.currentRole: CS & Applied Math @ Brown | KP Fellow
user.intro: Hello! I'm a rising sophomore on leave studying applied math and CS at Brown. I'm currently interning at Uber working on routing and maps and am a VP at Contrary! Previously, I worked at Skiff and Stream. Outside of tech, I enjoy journalism, speed chess, and Bay Area sports.

workExperiences.position: Engineering Project Manager, Visual Prosthesis Project
